---
title: Roasted Bacon and Squash Risotto with Spinach and Ricotta
description: Don't let "risotto" intimidate you, this dish is creamy, sweet and oh-so-easy! Roasted butternut squash, toasted almonds and creamy ricotta are here to make your date night dreams come true.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roasted-bacon-and-squash-risotto-df23ce32.jpg
